query:
SELECT
            remark,
            time_from AS "time_from: DateTime<Utc>",
            time_to AS "time_to: DateTime<Utc>"
        FROM adhoc_reservation
        WHERE
            time_to >= ?1 AND time_from < ?2 AND
            unit_id = ?3 AND
            (deleted_at IS NULL OR deleted_at > ?4)
